        <h2>Registration overview</h2>

        <p>Here is a very short introduction on how to register for EJC 2015. 
            And how to order additional goodies like more gala show tickets, 
            if you want :-)</p>

        <p>It's quite easy:</p>
        <ol>
            <li>Select a product, for example an EJC 2015 week ticket</li>
            <li>Provide the necessary information for your product (e.g. for the week ticket, we need the name and age of the juggler who will use the ticket)</li>
            <li>Add it to your shopping cart</li>
            <li>Repeat the previous steps as often as you like. If you want to buy three more week tickets for three friends, just add them to your shopping cart one after another.</li>
            <li>When you have added everything to your shopping cart, check it out: First tell us your contact information ("buyer") and how you want to pay, then confirm your order. That's it!</li>
